  <h2 class="sec">What you're adding your name to.</h2>
  <p class="lead">I believe living should not have a price tag.</p>
  <p>I believe technology should make life cheaper for everyone — not concentrate wealth for a few.</p>
  <p>I support using AI, robotics, and open tools to lower the real cost of food, shelter, energy, and the other essentials of a decent life.</p>
  <p>I stand for work that is a choice, not a sentence served just to survive.</p>
  <p>I add my name to call for a world where the basics of life are within everyone's reach.</p>
